_sText:
Mg_smee_tower.


The map is a big tower when the terrorist are in the top. Counter-terrorist are down. 
In the tower u can only come on the first floor, last floor and roof.

Terrorist spawn top tower. 25 spawn places
Counter-terrorist spawns on outside and inside 25 spawn places
There is a elevator
There are 2 ladders, 1 outside and 1 inside.
After 3 minutes console message saids "50 seconds left untill nuke launch"
After 4 minutes nuke comes and kill everyone that on the map.

Prefab use:
Unique - Pool Prefab
Mathijs - Office prefab (prefab that i made)

Any bugs on the map let me know it.
